texts.text: *Shouts*
*Roars*
Guess we have no choice.
*Growls*

>They defeat the summoned demons
one after another.
>But there's no end to them!

Ah, yes! That's it! That's the
spirit!

Damn it. The more we defeat,
the stronger Mithras gets!
But we have no choice!
I know!

Did he summon so many demons
because we're here, too?

Or would he have done this even
if Hikaru were alone?

I'm feeling pretty used, either
way!
*Bellows*

Jeng Yun! The last one went over
that way!
I'm on it!
Got you!
*Grunts, Groans*
>All the demons have vanished.

>And all the remaining power is
absorbed into Mithras...
My thanks, humans.

I never hoped to gather so much
power so swiftly. It is divine.

Yes, untold power stirs within
me again. It runneth over...

Listen to me, Hikaru. And you
humans over there.

I invite you to join me for the
final ritual.
The final ritual?

The ritual to revive Mithras.
To begin a new world.
Yes. It's finally time.

I will wait farther ahead. Join
me on the floor below.
Until then.
Wait, Mithras!
>With that, he vanishes.
Aaand he's gone.
So?

Are you really going through
with this, Hikaru?

You still haven't answered my
question from earlier.
I don't care what you say.

I want to start a new world.
For humanity's sake.

If there's a chance to end the
suffering, I'll take it.
A chance, huh?

Do whatever you like. Come
if you want.

But if you don't come, then
please, get Akari out of here.
>Hikaru takes his leave.
What should we do, Megakin?

That's obvious, ain't it? We
stop Hikaru and Mithras.

We dunno what this "chance" he's
taking could bring.

We can't let that affect
everyone else in the world.
Agreed.

I can't say I don't see where
he's coming from.

But what he's trying to do is
too extreme.

I don't think he understands the
responsibility he's taking on.
Yup.

Oughta trust the fellowship of
humanity, not demons.

The differences in our beliefs
are one reason to stop him.

But we should also stop Hikaru
for his own good.
That's what my gut says.

Then let's be off, Megakin.
Let's put a stop to this.

Aight, brace yourselves, boys!
Let's go!

>Venturing deeper, they
come upon a strange sight.

What is this? I can barely stand
this brightness.
And it's so hot.

The light's coming from... No,
the space itself is shining.
And there's a weird echo.

Sounds like lots of voices
on top of each other.
Hey, guys! You came!
Hikaru. Listen.

We're not here to chat. We came
to stop you.

What's with this place? All the
light and sounds?

Everything here is to help
revive Mithras.
Light is the power of faith.

The voices belong to people
who recognize Mithras as God.

Mithras is the one true king.
Haven't you heard?

Wait. You mean the deleted
part of that viral video?

Yep. Only people open to Mithras
saw that part.

That spread his name and fame.
Gave him strength.

You know how it works, don't
you? Belief makes gods stronger.

That video showed how many
people could be converted.

It's a lot if you include those
subconsciously influenced.

I see. So Mithras was behind the
spread of the video.
Why? For a big, public ritual?

Heck, no. Nothing fancy like
that.

Only his believers know about
his rituals.
I don't even know much, myself.

He can explain once he's revived
and outside the Aura Gate.

But it's pretty wild he can do all
this, right?

Some things really are beyond
human understanding.

Yet, this was no ordinary feat
for an ordinary deity.

It was done by my hand. The hand
of the one true God.
That voice. So, you're Mithras!
Yes, it is I, Mithras.

You did well to make it this
far, humans.

Everything is in order. All that
remains is the ritual.

The Sun God need no longer
smolder in shadow!
Hold on, Mithras!

I gotta ask. Why do you wanna be
revived so badly?
Why?

You need ask? I am owed faith.
I am owed obeisance.

Believers sought me in droves,
once.
And their many lives I saved.
But that... That other "God."
Because of His angels!
You mean...

My believers were punished and
oppressed!

I die and return each year. Yet
my day of rebirth was stolen!
I could no longer be revived!
What cruelty. What agony!

Yet, now you know how many
people want me, need me!
You mean, the viral video?

But it only went viral because
you used your demonic powers!

No! They all secretly long
for my return.

I knew they would accept me into
their hearts. I knew it.

This sun will not be chased
into the dark again. Ever.
As God, I will change the world.

I will construct a new world and
save humanity!
For I am the one true God!
Slow down, Mithras!

Humans! Behold my secret ritual
of resurrection!

With this I shall regain my full
powers!
*Bellows*

>Mithras starts absorbing all
the light in the area!

>He grows bigger and bigger as
it flows into him!

I feel it again, at last! This
sweet, blessed power.

O Mithras. Does this mean
my dream...
Yes, yes!

I will impose a new order on
this cruel world!
And thenãƒ¼
Wait just one second!
